node.content-desc: GitHub - Baseflow/PhotoView: Implementation of ImageView for Android that supports zooming, by various touch gestures.
Implementation of ImageView for Android that supports zooming, by various touch gestures.
PhotoView aims to help produce an easily usable implementation of a zooming Android ImageView.
Add this in your root build.gradle file (notyour module build.gradle file):
Then, add the library to your modulebuild.gradle
Out of the box zooming, using multi-touch and double-tap.
Works perfectly when used in a scrolling parent (such as ViewPager).
Allows the application to be notified when the displayed Matrix has changed. Useful for when you need to update your UI based on the current zoom/scroll position.
Allows the application to be notified when the user taps on the Photo.
